title: Matt Ramsey Of Old Dominion Talks About His Recent ER Visit + Jordan Davis Stops By To Perform His No. 1’s + Fun Fact Friday-Off: Amy vs. Eddie!
itunes:title: Matt Ramsey Of Old Dominion Talks About His Recent ER Visit + Jordan Davis Stops By To Perform His No. 1’s + Fun Fact Friday-Off: Amy vs. Eddie!
description:
Bobby talks to Matt Ramsey about his recent accident that sent him to the ER. Matt reveals what happened exactly and how he thought he was going to die. Jordan Davis stops by and performs a few of his no. 1’s for us and his current single on the radio. Amy takes on Eddie in the Fun Fact Friday Face off.
